(10540, 'No Prefix', 325000, 'Freehold', 'Detached', 'Hidden', 4, '15 WILLAND MOOR ROAD, WILLAND', 'Willand Moor Road, Willand', 'EX15 2SZ', '<ul>\r\n<li>Superior detached family home</li>\r\n<li>Adjoining and overlooking "village green"</li>\r\n<li>3 reception rooms</li>\r\n<li>Superb family kitchen/breakfast/living room</li>\r\n<li>Master suite with dressing room and ensuite shower</li>\r\n<li>Guest suite/bedroom 2 with ensuite</li>\r\n<li>Family bathroom</li>\r\n<li>2 further double bedrooms</li>\r\n<li>Walled garden</li>\r\n<li>Double garage with adjoining parking</li>\r\n<li>Gas central heating, UPVc double glazing</li>\r\n</ul>', '<p style="text-align: justify;"><span lang="en-GB">Impressive top of the range modern detached family home enjoying a corner plot adjoining and overlooking the traditional &ldquo;village green&rdquo; with Victorian style wrought iron railings and several fine mature oak trees.&nbsp; Oaks View offers lots of space for the growing family with its three fine reception rooms, superb family kitchen/breakfasting/living room and utility on the ground floor.&nbsp; Upstairs the opulent master suite provides a well appointed dressing room in addition to an ensuite shower room and a guest bedroom also features an ensuite shower with a family bathroom serving the remaining two double bedrooms.&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;">On the ground floor</p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span lang="en-GB">Georgian style portico to heavy panelled front door.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span lang="en-GB">Stunning U shaped central </span><span lang="en-GB">Hallway </span><span lang="en-GB">timber strip effect flooring having impressive straight staircase.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span lang="en-GB">Cloakroom</span><span lang="en-GB"> with white suite and window.</span></p>\r\n<p style="text-align: justify;"><span lang="en-GB">Sitting room</span><s