(10518, 'No Prefix', 110, 'Rental', 'Commercial', 'Viewing', 0, 'The Old Cattle Shed (Magnum House)', 'Sampford Peverell, Devon', 'EX16 7EG', '<ul>\r\n<li>Office Premises</li>\r\n<li>In a prominent accessible location, just half a mile from the M5 Motorway, North Devon link road and Tiverton Parkway Rail Station</li>\r\n<li>Newly refurbished office premises, 725&nbsp; - 1582 sq ft (gross)</li>\r\n<li>&pound;110 per week</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '<p><strong>SITUATION AND AMENITIES:</strong></p>\r\n<p>In a prominent location on the access to Tiverton Parkway rail station and within half a mile of Junction 27 on the M5 motorway where the North Devon link road commences.&nbsp; Exeter 18 miles, Taunton 13 miles.</p>\r\n<p><strong>ACCOMMODATION:</strong></p>\r\n<p>The premises form part of a building which has recently undergone a scheme of refurbishment and insulation to form modern office space with 2&nbsp;offices&nbsp;and work area&nbsp;shown shown on the floor plan herewith. (the remaining offices in the building have been let).</p>\r\n<p><strong>OUTSIDE:</strong></p>\r\n<p>There is ample parking space.</p>\r\n<p><strong>SERVICES:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Main water, electricity, private drainage.</p>\r\n<p><strong>BUSINESS RATES:</strong></p>\r\n<p>Rateable value &pound;4,450.&nbsp; (Occupiers qualifying for small business relief are unlikely to be required to pay business rates - but confirmation shoudl be obtained from the Mid Devon District Council).</p>\r\n<p><strong>LEASE:</strong></p>\r\n<p>The accommodation is available on internal repairing and insuring terms at a rent of &pound;138 per week.</p>\r\n<p>The cost of preparation of the lease will be payable by the tenant.</p>\r\n<p><strong>VIEWING:</strong></p>\r\n<p>By appointment please with Messrs Thorne &amp; Carter.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 2460, NULL, NULL, '0000-00-00', 'Y', 'Y', ' per week', 'N', 'N', 'N', '', '', '', ''),
