(10525, 'No Prefix', 15000, 'Rental', 'Commercial', 'Let', 0, 'Tourist Information Centre', 'Phoenix Lane, Tiverton', 'EX16 6LU', '<ul>\r\n<li>Town Centre, Tiverton&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li>in a Piazza Style Setting</li>\r\n<li>Shop (Former Tourist Information Building), 900 sq ft</li>\r\n<li>Offering an excellent location for coffee room/restaurant and possibly takeaway</li>\r\n</ul>', '<p><span lang="en-GB">In a lovely piazza style setting with sett paving, street sculpture and ornamental trees just off the centre of the town between the main shopping area of Fore Street and Marks and Spencer''s Supermarket, Mid Devon District Council Offices, multi-storey car park and coach station - all within 200m and therefore carrying a heavy footfall in this most desirable spacious yet busy pedestrianised area and offering an excellent location for coffee room/restaurant and possibly takeaway. </span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="en-GB"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-weight: bold; language: en-GB; mso-default-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-latin-font-family: Arial; mso-greek-font-family: Arial; mso-cyrillic-font-family: Arial; mso-hebrew-font-family: Arial; mso-arabic-font-family: Arial; mso-latinext-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: en-GB;" lang="en-GB">SITUATION &amp; AMENITIES: </span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; language: en-GB; mso-default-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-latin-font-family: Arial; mso-greek-font-family: Arial; mso-cyrillic-font-family: Arial; mso-hebrew-font-family: Arial; mso-arabic-font-family: Arial; mso-latinext-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: en-GB;" lang="en-GB">( please note distances are approximate).</span></span></p>\r\n<div class="shape" style="padding: 2.88pt;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; language: en-GB; mso-default-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-latin-font-family: Arial; mso-greek-font-family: Arial; mso-cyrillic-font-family: Arial; mso-hebrew-font-family: Arial; mso-arabic-font-family: Arial; mso-latinext-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: en-GB;" lang="en-GB">Tiverton is a market country town with a resident population of about 20,000 and a large rural catchment area beyond.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp; </span>It is approximately 15 miles north of Exeter and 22 miles from Taunton and served by the North Devon Link road and Junction 27 of the M5.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp; </span>As well as a thriving central retail area with wide pedestrianised Fore Street there is a good commercial and manufacturing base.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp; </span></span>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-justify: newspaper; text-align: justify; text-kashida-space: 50%; mso-pagination: none;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-justify: newspaper; text-align: justify; text-kashida-space: 50%; mso-pagination: none;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; language: en-GB; mso-default-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-latin-font-family: Arial; mso-greek-font-family: Arial; mso-cyrillic-font-family: Arial; mso-hebrew-font-family: Arial; mso-arabic-font-family: Arial; mso-latinext-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: en-GB;" lang="en-GB">A particularly</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center; mso-pagination: none;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; font-weight: bold; language: en-GB; mso-default-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-latin-font-family: Arial; mso-greek-font-family: Arial; mso-cyrillic-font-family: Arial; mso-hebrew-font-family: Arial; mso-arabic-font-family: Arial; mso-latinext-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: en-GB;" lang="en-GB">ATTRACTIVE TOWN CENTRE RETAIL PREMISES</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center; mso-pagination: none;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-justify: newspaper; text-align: justify; text-kashida-space: 50%; mso-pagination: none;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; language: en-GB; mso-default-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-latin-font-family: Arial; mso-greek-font-family: Arial; mso-cyrillic-font-family: Arial; mso-hebrew-font-family: Arial; mso-arabic-font-family: Arial; mso-latinext-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: en-GB;" lang="en-GB">Well suited for coffee shop, restaurant and associated similar uses or offices.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-justify: newspaper; text-align: justify; text-kashida-space: 50%; mso-pagination: none;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-justify: newspaper; text-align: justify; text-kashida-space: 50%; mso-pagination: none;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; language: en-GB; mso-default-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-latin-font-family: Arial; mso-greek-font-family: Arial; mso-cyrillic-font-family: Arial; mso-hebrew-font-family: Arial; mso-arabic-font-family: Arial; mso-latinext-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: en-GB;" lang="en-GB">Of facing brick elevations under a natural slate roof, attractively extended with glazed canopy eaves, the building has extensive window displays on three sides and lofty sloping pine clad ceiling</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-justify: newspaper; text-align: justify; text-kashida-space: 50%; mso-pagination: none;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-justify: newspaper; text-align: justify; text-kashida-space: 50%; mso-pagination: none;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; language: en-GB; mso-default-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-latin-font-family: Arial; mso-greek-font-family: Arial; mso-cyrillic-font-family: Arial; mso-hebrew-font-family: Arial; mso-arabic-font-family: Arial; mso-latinext-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: en-GB;" lang="en-GB"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp;</span>in all extending to approximately </span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; text-decoration: underline; language: en-GB; mso-default-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-latin-font-family: Arial; mso-greek-font-family: Arial; mso-cyrillic-font-family: Arial; mso-hebrew-font-family: Arial; mso-arabic-font-family: Arial; mso-latinext-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: en-GB; text-underline: single;" lang="en-GB">900 sq ft. (Gross internal floor area) </span><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; language: en-GB; mso-default-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-latin-font-family: Arial; mso-greek-font-family: Arial; mso-cyrillic-font-family: Arial; mso-hebrew-font-family: Arial; mso-arabic-font-family: Arial; mso-latinext-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: en-GB;" lang="en-GB">and comprises:</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-justify: newspaper; text-align: justify; text-kashida-space: 50%; mso-pagination: none;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-justify: newspaper; text-align: justify; text-kashida-space: 50%; mso-pagination: none;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; language: en-GB; mso-default-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-latin-font-family: Arial; mso-greek-font-family: Arial; mso-cyrillic-font-family: Arial; mso-hebrew-font-family: Arial; mso-arabic-font-family: Arial; mso-latinext-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: en-GB;" lang="en-GB">SHOP AREA<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp; </span>20&rsquo;6&rdquo; x 31&rsquo; max with central double entrance doors, lofty pine timbered ceiling, display windows, electric storage heater, curtain heater, entrance doors, curtain heater, Comfort-Aire fan assisted unit heater, fluorescent light fan.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-justify: newspaper; text-align: justify; text-kashida-space: 50%; mso-pagination: none;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; language: en-GB; mso-default-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-latin-font-family: Arial; mso-greek-font-family: Arial; mso-cyrillic-font-family: Arial; mso-hebrew-font-family: Arial; mso-arabic-font-family: Arial; mso-latinext-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: en-GB;" lang="en-GB">internal LOBBY area</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-justify: newspaper; text-align: justify; text-kashida-space: 50%; mso-pagination: none;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; language: en-GB; mso-default-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-latin-font-family: Arial; mso-greek-font-family: Arial; mso-cyrillic-font-family: Arial; mso-hebrew-font-family: Arial; mso-arabic-font-family: Arial; mso-latinext-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: en-GB;" lang="en-GB">KITCHENETTE 10&rsquo;4&rdquo; x 7&rsquo;5&rdquo; with sink unit and external door and heater stockroom, 9&rsquo;10&rdquo; x 15&rsquo;3&rdquo;2&rdquo;</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-justify: newspaper; text-align: justify; text-kashida-space: 50%; mso-pagination: none;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; language: en-GB; mso-default-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-latin-font-family: Arial; mso-greek-font-family: Arial; mso-cyrillic-font-family: Arial; mso-hebrew-font-family: Arial; mso-arabic-font-family: Arial; mso-latinext-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: en-GB;" lang="en-GB">DISABLED TOILET of WC with wash basin AND PANEL HEATER</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-justify: newspaper; text-align: justify; text-kashida-space: 50%; mso-pagination: none;"><span style="font-family: Arial; color: black; language: en-GB; mso-default-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-latin-font-family: Arial; mso-greek-font-family: Arial; mso-cyrillic-font-family: Arial; mso-hebrew-font-family: Arial; mso-arabic-font-family: Arial; mso-latinext-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: en-GB;" lang="en-GB">OFFICE 9&rsquo;10&rdquo; x 9&rsquo;9&rdquo;</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-justify: inter-word; text-align: justify; mso-pagination: none;"><span style="font-family: Arial; language: en-GB; mso-default-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-latin-font-family: Arial; mso-greek-font-family: Arial; mso-cyrillic-font-family: Arial; mso-hebrew-font-family: Arial; mso-arabic-font-family: Arial; mso-latinext-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: en-GB;" lang="en-GB">SEPARATE FORMER OFFICE 12&rsquo;5&rdquo; max overall with sink unit and including separate WC, facing the bus station and easily accommodated into the main shop area by the formation of an opening or, alternatively, used separately.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-justify: inter-word; text-align: justify; mso-pagination: none;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-justify: inter-word; text-align: justify; mso-pagination: none;"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-weight: bold; language: en-GB; mso-default-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-latin-font-family: Arial; mso-greek-font-family: Arial; mso-cyrillic-font-family: Arial; mso-hebrew-font-family: Arial; mso-arabic-font-family: Arial; mso-latinext-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: en-GB;" lang="en-GB">OUTSIDE:<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family: Arial; language: en-GB; mso-default-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-latin-font-family: Arial; mso-greek-font-family: Arial; mso-cyrillic-font-family: Arial; mso-hebrew-font-family: Arial; mso-arabic-font-family: Arial; mso-latinext-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: en-GB;" lang="en-GB">Glazed canopy 3&rsquo;6&rdquo; wide around much of the premises which affords the opportunity for external tables and seating for say 24 covers.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp; </span>It may be possible to obtain for more outside table space by licence. </span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-justify: inter-word; text-align: justify; mso-pagination: none;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-justify: inter-word; text-align: justify; mso-pagination: none;"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-weight: bold; language: en-GB; mso-default-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-latin-font-family: Arial; mso-greek-font-family: Arial; mso-cyrillic-font-family: Arial; mso-hebrew-font-family: Arial; mso-arabic-font-family: Arial; mso-latinext-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: en-GB;" lang="en-GB">SERVICES:<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family: Arial; language: en-GB; mso-default-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-latin-font-family: Arial; mso-greek-font-family: Arial; mso-cyrillic-font-family: Arial; mso-hebrew-font-family: Arial; mso-arabic-font-family: Arial; mso-latinext-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: en-GB;" lang="en-GB">Main water electricity and drainage are connected .</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-justify: inter-word; text-align: justify; mso-pagination: none;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-justify: inter-word; text-align: justify; mso-pagination: none;"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-weight: bold; language: en-GB; mso-default-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-latin-font-family: Arial; mso-greek-font-family: Arial; mso-cyrillic-font-family: Arial; mso-hebrew-font-family: Arial; mso-arabic-font-family: Arial; mso-latinext-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: en-GB;" lang="en-GB">PLANNING: </span><span style="font-family: Arial; language: en-GB; mso-default-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-latin-font-family: Arial; mso-greek-font-family: Arial; mso-cyrillic-font-family: Arial; mso-hebrew-font-family: Arial; mso-arabic-font-family: Arial; mso-latinext-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: en-GB;" lang="en-GB">The Unit has the benefit of planning consent for the previous use as a tourist information centre but it is assumed that planning consent would be available for restaurant, office or similar uses.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp; </span>Interested parties should make their own enquiries of the planning authority, Mid Devon District Council.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-justify: inter-word; text-align: justify; mso-pagination: none;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-justify: inter-word; text-align: justify; mso-pagination: none;"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-weight: bold; language: en-GB; mso-default-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-latin-font-family: Arial; mso-greek-font-family: Arial; mso-cyrillic-font-family: Arial; mso-hebrew-font-family: Arial; mso-arabic-font-family: Arial; mso-latinext-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: en-GB;" lang="en-GB">RATEABLE VALUE:<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp; </span></span><span style="font-family: Arial; language: en-GB; mso-default-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-latin-font-family: Arial; mso-greek-font-family: Arial; mso-cyrillic-font-family: Arial; mso-hebrew-font-family: Arial; mso-arabic-font-family: Arial; mso-latinext-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: en-GB;" lang="en-GB">The premises are assessed as two separate hereditaments viz &pound;10,250.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp;&nbsp; </span>Separate Office &pound;490.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-justify: inter-word; text-align: justify; mso-pagination: none;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-justify: inter-word; text-align: justify; mso-pagination: none;"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-weight: bold; language: en-GB; mso-default-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-latin-font-family: Arial; mso-greek-font-family: Arial; mso-cyrillic-font-family: Arial; mso-hebrew-font-family: Arial; mso-arabic-font-family: Arial; mso-latinext-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: en-GB;" lang="en-GB">TERM</span><span style="font-family: Arial; language: en-GB; mso-default-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-latin-font-family: Arial; mso-greek-font-family: Arial; mso-cyrillic-font-family: Arial; mso-hebrew-font-family: Arial; mso-arabic-font-family: Arial; mso-latinext-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: en-GB;" lang="en-GB">: A long term lease is envisaged. </span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-justify: inter-word; text-align: justify; mso-pagination: none;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-justify: inter-word; text-align: justify; mso-pagination: none;"><span style="font-family: Arial; font-weight: bold; language: en-GB; mso-default-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-latin-font-family: Arial; mso-greek-font-family: Arial; mso-cyrillic-font-family: Arial; mso-hebrew-font-family: Arial; mso-arabic-font-family: Arial; mso-latinext-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: en-GB;" lang="en-GB">RENT</span><span style="font-family: Arial; language: en-GB; mso-default-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-latin-font-family: Arial; mso-greek-font-family: Arial; mso-cyrillic-font-family: Arial; mso-hebrew-font-family: Arial; mso-arabic-font-family: Arial; mso-latinext-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: en-GB;" lang="en-GB">: &pound;15,000<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp; </span>Per annum (we understand that no Value Added Tax is payable).<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-justify: inter-word; text-align: justify; mso-pagination: none;"><span style="font-family: Arial; language: en-GB; mso-default-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-latin-font-family: Arial; mso-greek-font-family: Arial; mso-cyrillic-font-family: Arial; mso-hebrew-font-family: Arial; mso-arabic-font-family: Arial; mso-latinext-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: en-GB;" lang="en-GB">The main former Tourist Information Centre Premises are available at a rent of &pound;15,000 per annum.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-justify: inter-word; text-align: justify; mso-pagination: none;"><span style="font-family: Arial; language: en-GB; mso-default-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-latin-font-family: Arial; mso-greek-font-family: Arial; mso-cyrillic-font-family: Arial; mso-hebrew-font-family: Arial; mso-arabic-font-family: Arial; mso-latinext-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: en-GB;" lang="en-GB">The adjoining separate office is available by negotiation in addition or separately.</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-justify: inter-word; text-align: justify; mso-pagination: none;"><span style="font-family: Arial; language: en-GB; mso-default-font-family: Arial; mso-ascii-font-family: Arial; mso-latin-font-family: Arial; mso-greek-font-family: Arial; mso-cyrillic-font-family: Arial; mso-hebrew-font-family: Arial; mso-arabic-font-family: Arial; mso-latinext-font-family: Arial; mso-ansi-language: en-GB;" lang="en-GB">The premises are available on a full repairing and insuring lease.<span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination: none;"><span style="language: en-GB;" lang="en-GB">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="shape" style="padding: 2.88pt;">&nbsp;</div>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 2447, NULL, NULL, '0000-00-00', 'Y', 'Y', 'per annum', 'N', 'N', 'N', '', '', '', ''),
(10681, 'No Prefix', 179950, 'Freehold', 'Semi', 'Sale Agreed', 3, '2 Stile Court', 'Colebrook Lane, Cullompton', 'EX15 1PB', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>A delightfully presented semi detached home&nbsp;a short walk from the High Street shops.&nbsp; The property boasts 3 bedrooms, , a good size sitting room, kitchen breakfast room and conservatory.</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span lang="en-GB">Conveniently situated for high street shops and supermarkets with secondary and primary schooling being within about a ten minute walk.&nbsp; Cullompton also boasts two doctors surgeries, library, community centre, sport centre and Padbrook Golf Course and leisure centre.&nbsp; The M5 passes the town and provides a rapid link with Exeter to the south and Taunton to the north.&nbsp; The nearby Blackdown Hills is designated as an Area of Outstanding Natural Beauty and provides walking and a wealth of other rural pursuits.&nbsp; The comparatively central Mid Devon location places the picturesque National Parks of Dartmoor and Exmoor together with north and south Devon coastlines all within a modest car journey.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span lang="en-GB">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;<span lang="en-GB">Superbly presented modern semi detached home</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;<span lang="en-GB">Gas central heating and UPVc double glazing</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;<span lang="en-GB">Hall with cloakroom</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;<span lang="en-GB">Sitting room</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;<span lang="en-GB">Kitchen/breakfast room</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;<span lang="en-GB">Conservatory</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;<span lang="en-GB">Three bedrooms</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;<span lang="en-GB">Refitted bathroom</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;<span lang="en-GB">South facing gardens</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;<span lang="en-GB">Parking</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;<span lang="en-GB">15 miles Exeter, 18 miles Taunton</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;<span lang="en-GB">Tiverton Parkway Railway Station 6 miles</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;<span lang="en-GB">Exeter International Airport 15 miles</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;<span lang="en-GB">Main electricity, water, gas and drainage</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span lang="en-GB">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span lang="en-GB">On the ground floor</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span lang="en-GB">Canopy entrance porch with tiled roof to half glazed UPVc front door to </span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span lang="en-GB">Hall</span><span lang="en-GB"> radiator, coat hooks.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span lang="en-GB">Cloakroom</span><span lang="en-GB"> modern white suite comprising pedestal basin, close coupled WC, half tiled walls, timber effect flooring, window, chrome ladder style towel rail/radiator.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span lang="en-GB">Sitting Room</span><span lang="en-GB"> bright and airy room having deep understair recess, stone effect feature fireplace and hearth, television shelving to one side, radiator.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span lang="en-GB">Kitchen/Breakfast Room</span><span lang="en-GB"> lovely south facing room, the kitchen area being fitted with extensive range of pale timber effect laminate fronted units comprising base cupboards, drawer pack, tall cupboard, marble effect work top with inset Asterite single drainer sink, mixer tap, free standing Rangemaster 55 cooker with four ring hob, oven and grill below, wall cupboard, contemporary bevelled edged tiling, timber effect flooring, space and plumbing for washing machine, outlook over rear garden, wall mounted Vaillant gas boiler. The </span><span lang="en-GB">Dining </span><span lang="en-GB">end being carpeted with radiator and sliding double glazed patio door to </span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span lang="en-GB">Conservatory</span><span lang="en-GB"> of UPVc construction, double glazed, French door to gardens.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span lang="en-GB">Turning stairs to </span><span lang="en-GB">Landing</span><span lang="en-GB"> access to loft, airing cupboard with factory lagged hot water cylinder, slatted shelving.</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="en-GB">Bedroom 1</span><span lang="en-GB"> radiator, outlook over rear garden and views to Bradninch Hill and Golf Course.</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="en-GB">Bedroom 2</span><span lang="en-GB"> radiator, one wall entirely fitted with wardrobes with sliding mirrored doors.</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="en-GB">Bedroom 3</span><span lang="en-GB"> radiator, views to Bradninch Hill and Golf Course.</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="en-GB">Bathroom </span><span lang="en-GB">recently refitted with stylish white suite comprising bath with mixer tap/shower attachment over, vanity washbasin with cupboard beneath, close coupled WC, half tiled walls, bathroom cabinet, extractor fan, window, timber effect flooring, chrome ladder style radiator/towel rail, electric shaver point.</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="en-GB">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="en-GB">Outside</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="en-GB">South facing rear garden mainly hard landscaped with areas of gravel and paving stones, inset borders and shrubs, built in brick BBQ, two garden </span><span lang="en-GB">Sheds.</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="en-GB"> Wisteria clad rustic arch, fully fenced with pedestrian gate to parking.</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="mso-pagination: none;"><span style="language: en-GB; mso-ligatures: none;" lang="en-GB">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: justify; -ms-text-justify: newspaper; -ms-text-kashida-space: 50%; mso-pagination: none;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align