ight v:ext="view" color="black [0]" color2="white [7]"/>\r\n   <o:bottom v:ext="view" color="black [0]" color2="white [7]"/>\r\n   <o:column v:ext="view" color="black [0]" color2="white [7]"/>\r\n  </v:stroke>\r\n  <v:shadow color="black [0]"/>\r\n  <o:extrusion v:ext="view" backdepth="0" viewpoint="0,0" viewpointorigin="0,0"/>\r\n  <v:textbox inset="2.88pt,2.88pt,2.88pt,2.88pt"/>\r\n  <o:colormenu v:ext="edit" fillcolor="blue [1]" strokecolor="black [0]"\r\n   shadowcolor="#ccc [4]"/>\r\n </o:shapedefaults><o:shapelayout v:ext="edit">\r\n  <o:idmap v:ext="edit" data="1"/>\r\n </o:shapelayout></xml><![endif]--></p>\r\n<p><span lang="en-GB">Pleasantly located towards the outskirts of Cullompton with its range of High Street Shops,&nbsp; two supermarkets, two doctors surgeries, two primary schools and secondary school.&nbsp; The M5 passes the town and facilitates rapid commuting south to the Cathedral City of Exeter and north to the county town of Taunton.&nbsp; The surrounding countryside offers a wealth of rural&nbsp; pursuits with the nearby Blackdown Hills being designated as an Area of Outstanding Natural Beauty.&nbsp; The town&nbsp; also boasts a newly built library and stunning community centre in addition to the fine Grade I listed St Andrews Church and newly restored medieval house known as the Walronds.&nbsp; The comparatively central Mid Devon location places the picturesque National Parks of Dartmoor and Exmoor together with north and south Devon coastlines all within a modest car journey.&nbsp; </span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="en-GB">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;<span lang="en-GB">Solar Array installed 2012 providing &pound;1,512 feed </span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="en-GB">&nbsp;&nbsp; in tariff over the last </span></p>\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;<span lang="en-GB">Gas central heating and UPVc double glazing</span></p>\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;<span lang="en-GB">Hall with cloakroom</span></p>\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;<span lang="en-GB">Two receptions</span></p>\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;<span lang="en-GB">Kitchen and huge utility room</span></p>\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;<span lang="en-GB">Conservatory</span></p>\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;<span lang="en-GB">Three bedrooms, Shower room.</span></p>\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;<span lang="en-GB">Garage, Large established gardens, views.</span></p>\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;<span lang="en-GB">15 miles Exeter, 18 miles Taunton</span></p>\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;<span lang="en-GB">Tiverton Parkway Railway Station 6 miles</span></p>\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;<span lang="en-GB">Exeter International Airport 15 miles</span></p>\r\n<p>&middot;&nbsp;<span lang="en-GB">Main electricity, water, gas and drainage</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="en-GB">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="en-GB">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="en-GB">On the ground floor</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="en-GB">Canopy entrance porch to part glazed UPVc front door.</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="en-GB">Hall</span><span lang="en-GB"> radiator, understairs cupboard, central heating thermostat control.</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="en-GB">Cloakroom</span><span lang="en-GB"> with white suite comprising WC, washbasin, coathooks, radiator, window.</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="en-GB">Sitting Room</span><span lang="en-GB"> wide picture window enjoying outlook across the valley, radiator, fireplace and hearth with open grate, shelving to alcove.</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="en-GB">Dining Room</span><span lang="en-GB"> radiator, door to conservatory, the partition between sitting room and dining room is a lightweight construction and could readily be removed to reinstate the original lounge dining room.</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="en-GB">Kitchen</span><span lang="en-GB"> range of pale timber effect units comprising 6 base cupboards, integrated refrigerator, marble effect roll edged worktops, inset stainless steel single drainer sink, 4 wall cupboards, fully tiled, free standing Parkinson Cowan cooker with 4 ring gas hob and electric oven under, eye level grill, shelved larder cupboard.</span></p>\r\n<p><span lang="en-GB">Utility Room</span><span lang="en-GB"> work top with base cupboard beneath, stainless steel single drainer sink, space and plumbing for washing machine and dishwasher, L-shaped range of units matching those in the kitchen and comprising tall larder cupboard, tall broom cupboard with shelving, 4 base cupboards, additional work top, wall mounted Maxi gas boiler, half glazed UPVc back door, space for tumble dryer.</span></p>\r\n<p><br /><!--[if !mso]>\r\n<style>\r\nv\\:* {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\r\no\\:* {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\r\nb\\:* {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\r\n.shape {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\r\n</style>\r\n<![endif]--></p>\r\n<p><!--[if pub]><xml>\r\n <b:Publication type="OplPub" oty="68" oh="256">\r\n  <b:OhPrintBlock priv="30E">281</b:OhPrintBlock>\r\n  <b:NuDefaultUnits priv="1004">1</b:NuDefaultUnits>\r\n  <b:DptlPageDimensions type="OplPt" priv="1211">\r\n   <b:Xl priv="104">7560000</b:Xl>\r\n   <b:Yl priv="204">10692000</b:Yl>\r\n  </b:DptlPageDimensions>\r\n  <b:DxlDefaultTab priv="1504">359410</b:DxlDefaultTab>\r\n  <b:OhGallery priv="180E">259</b:OhGallery>\r\n  <b:OhFancyBorders priv="190E">261</b:OhFancyBorders>\r\n  <b:OhCaptions priv="1A0E">257</b:OhCaptions>\r\n  <b:OhQuillDoc priv="200E">276</b:OhQuillDoc>\r\n  <b:OhMailMergeData priv="210E">262</b:OhMailMergeData>\r\n  <b:OhColorScheme priv="220E">279</b:OhColorScheme>\r\n  <b:DwNextUniqueOid priv="2304">1</b:DwNextUniqueOid>\r\n  <b:IdentGUID priv="2A07">0``````````````````````</b:IdentGUID>\r\n  <b:DpgSpecial priv="2C03">5</b:DpgSpecial>\r\n  <b:FWorkpaneVisible priv="3900">False</b:FWorkpaneVisible>\r\n  <b:CTimesEdited priv="3C04">1</b:CTimesEdited>\r\n  <b:NuDefaultUnitsEx priv="4104">1</b:NuDefaultUnitsEx>\r\n  <b:OhImpositionEngine priv="440E">285</b:OhImpositionEngine>\r\n </b:Publication>\r\n <b:PrinterInfo type="OplPrb" oty="75" oh="281">\r\n  <b:OhColorSepBlock priv="30E">282</b:OhColorSepBlock>\r\n  <b:FKOBlackFills