r\n  <o:idmap v:ext="edit" data="1"/>\r\n </o:shapelayout></xml><![endif]--></p>\r\n<p><span lang="en-GB">Constructed in 1898 this charming period home is set well back from Willand Road.&nbsp; Traditionally built of brick beneath a slate roof, improvements have included the installation of double glazed windows and gas fired central heating.&nbsp; The remarkably spacious accommodation is attractively arranged over three floors with the dining room and sitting room being linked by a wide archway.&nbsp; The kitchen with its hand painted units and utility room lie to the rear.&nbsp; The ground floor bathroom has the advantage of providing a ground floor toilet whilst at the same time allowing all three bedrooms to be generous doubles.&nbsp; An early inspection is strongly recommended to those seeking a characterful home with far more accommodation than would normally be found in a more expensive modern property.&nbsp; The owner is moving abroad and much of the furniture and fitments are available by negotiation.</span></p>\r\n<p><br /><!--[if !mso]>\r\n<style>\r\nv\\:* {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\r\no\\:* {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\r\nb\\:* {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\r\n.shape {behavior:url(#default#VML);}\r\n</style>\r\n<![endif]--></p>\r\n<p><!--[if pub]><xml>\r\n <b:Publication type="OplPub" oty="68" oh="256">\r\n  <b:OhPrintBlock priv="30E">281</b:OhPrintBlock>\r\n  <b:NuDefaultUnits priv="1004">1</b:NuDefaultUnits>\r\n  <b:DptlPageDimensions type="OplPt" priv="1211">\r\n   <b:Xl priv="104">7560000</b:Xl>\r\n   <b:Yl priv="204">10692000</b:Yl>\r\n  </b:DptlPageDimensions>\r\n  <b:DxlDefaultTab priv="1504">359410</b:DxlDefaultTab>\r\n  <b:OhGallery priv="180E">259</b:OhGallery>\r\n  <b:OhFancyBorders priv="190E">261</b:OhFancyBorders>\r\n  <b:OhCaptions priv="1A0E">257</b:OhCaptions>\r\n  <b:OhQuillDoc priv="200E">276</b:OhQuillDoc>\r\n  <b:OhMailMergeData priv="210E">262</b:OhMailMergeData>\r\n  <b:OhColorScheme priv="220E">279</b:OhColorScheme>\r\n  <b:Dw